Package: leafpop
Type: Package
Title: Include Tables, Images and Graphs in Leaflet Popups
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2019-04-05
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Tim",
             family = "Appelhans",
             role = c("cre", "aut"),
             email = "tim.appelhans@gmail.com"),
      person(given = "Florian",
             family = "Detsch",
             role = "aut",
             email = "fdetsch@web.de"))
Maintainer: Tim Appelhans <tim.appelhans@gmail.com>
Description: Creates HTML strings to embed tables, images or graphs in popups
  of interactive maps created with packages 'leaflet' or 'mapview'. Handles
  local paths to images on the file system or remote urls. Handles graphs created 
  with 'base' graphics, 'lattice' or 'ggplot2' as well as interactive plots created 
  with 'htmlwidgets'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: 
  base64enc,
  brew,
  gdalUtils,
  htmlwidgets,
  Rcpp (>= 1.0.0),
  svglite,
  uuid
Suggests:
  lattice,
  leaflet (>= 2.0.0),
  sf,
  sp
LinkingTo: Rcpp
